api_list.name: GetOlympiaData2021
api_list.description: Get all data from Olympia 2021 contest
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://olympia-contest-champions.p.rapidapi.com/OlympiaData2021"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "olympia-contest-champions.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
